item.description:
Membership Meeting, Tuesday May 3rd, 7:00 Rm 205 Comm Center
Join us as we discuss all the projects coming up over the spring months plus the ongoing efforts of the Paws in the Park and Wapping Fair. We will be helping make the bone bag prizes for paws in the park. In addition, we will be having a Paws orientation to review the different areas of Paws in the Park (contests, photos, crafts, tea cup auction, silent auction, etc.. so everyone has an understanding going into the day of theresponsibilities at the project. Light dinner being provided. RSVP on Meetup.
item.name: Membership Meeting
